### ğŸ›ï¸ User Interface  
- ğŸ” Browse available burgers  
- ğŸ§¾ Select addons dynamically (extra cheese, fries, sauces, etc.)  
- ğŸ›’ Add or remove items from cart  
- ğŸ’° View auto-calculated total and grand total  
- ğŸ“¦ Place orders â€” User can see past orders, instantly reflected on the admin panel.

### ğŸ§¾ Billing  
- âœ… Bill generation after successful order placement  
- ğŸ§® Auto calculation of burger + addons cost  

